Richard Stallman
Height: 112cm
Beard: 59cm
Richard is a software freedom activist, hacker, and software developer. He launched the GNU Project, he started the free software movement wrote the GPL and set up the Free Software Foundation. Stallman has spent most of his time kicking ass for free software, as well as disemboweling jerks who like software patents and what he sees as excessive extension of copyright laws. Stallman has also developed the original Emacs, the GNU Compiler Collection, and the GNU Debugger.  His beard is probably the greatest beard in software.
